City Defense
The Marshal, essentially a field general, isn't overly concerned about the safety of each soldier, but still prefers manpower to zombie armies. You can take his place and help the young and inexperienced soldiers survive the attacks of the animals driven mad by Firez's experiments. The city of Sadrok is well defended, but caution still doesn't hurt.
